Hi! I'm Hasna and I'll be attending and supporting TKMDII XIII, the biggest Interior Design event of the year!
.
TKMDII is an 'open for public' event organized by Interior Design students which is held once in 2 years.
.
EVENTS:
💫 K A R Y A  B A R U  B E R S A M A
An Installation made by 23 universities all across Indonesia.
🍗K A R Y A  B A R U  D E L E G A S I 
A collaboration between 21 PKL and 21 delegations to give you a whole new street-food hunting experience!
✏ S E M I N A R
Understanding deeper about the role and meaning of Tradition in Interior Design.
💡 W O R K S H O P
Understand more about local material, understanding more about surroundings and observing citizens' responds to design objects.
🚶‍♀E K S K U R S I
Walking around Bandung to get to know more about mesmerizing and phenomenal places around the town.
🔎M A T E R I A L  E X P O
Expanding your material knowledge.
✨A C A D E M I C A L  E X H I B I T I O N
Getting to know more about what Interior Designers create at the universities!
.
Come and be a part of the celebration on August 11&12th 2017 at Institut Teknologi Bandung! Open from 9am - 6pm.
.
